.IX Title "Moose::Cookbook::Meta::Labeled_AttributeTrait 3"
.TH Moose::Cookbook::Meta::Labeled_AttributeTrait 3 "2014-01-19" "perl v5.18.2" "User Contributed Perl Documentation"
